prompt: If Twizzlump(x,y) and Twizzlump(y,z) then what are the possible relationships between x and z?
answer:
### Answer:
The possible relations between x and z are exactly all of the base‐relations except Frooblenap.  In the given terminology:
Blorpticate(x,z) or Snarfloon(x,z) or Twizzlump(x,z) or Glimberish(x,z) or Crindlewop(x,z) or Narpulate(x,z) or Zindlequack(x,z).
